<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 01:30:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>策略通过更多炼金术在另一场比特币崩盘中幸存</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/strategy-survives-another-bitcoin-crash-with-more-alchemy</link><description>Michael Saylor 的比特币积累公司 Strategy Inc. 通过一些新的金融工程，在另一场加密货币市场崩溃中幸存下来。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i9OlmpClxkrY/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 15:54:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/strategy-survives-another-bitcoin-crash-with-more-alchemy</guid></item><item><title>“忧虑之墙”让散户观望最新的比特币反弹</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-05/-wall-of-worry-has-retail-sitting-out-the-latest-bitcoin-rally</link><description>衡量市场情绪的一个关键指标几周来一直闪烁着看跌信号。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQzk9y1NgXzQ/v6/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-05/-wall-of-worry-has-retail-sitting-out-the-latest-bitcoin-rally</guid></item><item><title>拥抱人工智能，否则就会落后：加密货币公司纷纷裁员</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/embrace-ai-or-get-left-behind-job-cuts-sweep-through-crypto-firms</link><description>加密货币和支付公司一系列与人工智能相关的裁员给分析师和投资者带来了一个好奇的问题：如何评估人工智能部分是否真实？ &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWniLtHgFScg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 19:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/embrace-ai-or-get-left-behind-job-cuts-sweep-through-crypto-firms</guid></item><item><title>Coinbase 以波动的市场和人工智能为由裁员 14%</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/coinbase-to-cut-14-of-workforce-citing-volatile-markets-ai</link><description>加密货币交易所 Coinbase Global Inc. 将裁员约 14%，理由是需要管理动荡市场的成本和人工智能技术进步。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iDpBBVhmfW64/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 11:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/coinbase-to-cut-14-of-workforce-citing-volatile-markets-ai</guid></item><item><title>Andreessen Horowitz 筹集 22 亿美元新加密货币基金</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/andreessen-horowitz-raises-new-2-2-billion-crypto-fund</link><description>Andreessen Horowitz 筹集了 22 亿美元的加密货币基金，在风险投资行业仍在恢复对该行业的兴趣之际，该基金加倍投资数字资产。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iTAyEgA5maMo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/andreessen-horowitz-raises-new-2-2-billion-crypto-fund</guid></item><item><title>人工智能最热门的私营公司拥有蓬勃发展的加密货币影子市场</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/ai-s-hottest-private-companies-have-booming-crypto-shadow-market</link><description>向散户投资者出售人工智能热潮的一部分的竞赛已经成为主流——封闭式基金、区间基金、特殊用途工具。现在，加密货币平台正在提供与地球上最有价值的私营人工智能公司相关的交易——普通投资者几乎没有其他方式可以参与这些交易。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/idJ8est2Gn.M/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 00:30:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/ai-s-hottest-private-companies-have-booming-crypto-shadow-market</guid></item><item><title>美元主导地位粉碎了拉加德的欧洲加密货币野心</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-05-04/global-crypto-race-why-divided-europe-is-losing-ground</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在货币未来的争夺中，美元拥有巨大的领先优势&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i1mTEn6hIX1g/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 21:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-05-04/global-crypto-race-why-divided-europe-is-losing-ground</guid></item><item><title>渣打银行的风险投资部门以 10 亿美元的估值支持加密货币公司 GSR</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/stanchart-s-vc-arm-backs-crypto-firm-gsr-at-1-billion-valuation</link><description>随着渣打银行进一步进军数字资产市场，渣打银行全资拥有的风险投资部门 SC Ventures 投资了加密货币交易公司 GSR。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ieadhEEYy72U/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 04:50:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/stanchart-s-vc-arm-backs-crypto-firm-gsr-at-1-billion-valuation</guid></item><item><title>银行集团称参议院稳定币奖励提案“不足”</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/bank-groups-say-senate-stablecoin-rewards-proposal-falls-short</link><description>银行集团周一推迟了一项加密货币市场结构提案，这加大了美国立法者继续就关键稳定币奖励条款进行谈判的压力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i8DHz477Madk/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 00:55:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/bank-groups-say-senate-stablecoin-rewards-proposal-falls-short</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚养老金体系内部的风险支点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/crypto-property-grow-in-australia-s-self-managed-funds-smsfs</link><description>&lt;p&gt;对退休的深深焦虑促使人们转向自助投资工具，他们在其中购买了加密货币和其他风险资产。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ikmOe9DG3alA/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 21:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/crypto-property-grow-in-australia-s-self-managed-funds-smsfs</guid></item><item><title>与特朗普相关的世界自由组织起诉孙宇晨诽谤</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/trump-linked-world-liberty-sues-justin-sun-for-defamation</link><description>世界自由金融公司表示，正在以诽谤罪起诉孙宇晨，指责这位亿万富翁加密货币企业家在上个月对特朗普相关项目提起诉讼后，针对该项目发起了协调一致的媒体宣传活动。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iAw0svHpP.xU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 13:08:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/trump-linked-world-liberty-sues-justin-sun-for-defamation</guid></item><item><title>比特币自 1 月份以来首次升至 80,000 美元以上</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/bitcoin-btc-tops-80-000-for-three-month-high-as-asian-stocks-rise</link><description>由于人们对达成协议以解决中东冲突扫清道路的预期不断波动，比特币自 1 月份以来首次突破 80,000 美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iw.jWHIx1AUg/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 02:58:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/bitcoin-btc-tops-80-000-for-three-month-high-as-asian-stocks-rise</guid></item></channel></rss>